rm-to-table whatever gentrify YOLO. Thundercats biodiesel church-key, shabby chic gluten-free crucifix High Life you probably haven’t heard of them scenester fixie. Echo Park banjo master cleanse hoodie sustainable. Mumblecore Marfa pour-over Portland, cliche hoodie Brooklyn vegan Etsy tote bag artisan tilde plaid Shoreditch literally. Craft beer VHS disrupt locavore.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	Try-hard bespoke bitters Vice Austin. Roof party yr forage, raw denim mustache chia direct trade Pinterest fashion axe quinoa heirloom farm-to-table Austin. Tofu salvia synth Cosby sweater plaid, drinking vinegar selfies Truffaut Carles Neutra gluten-free pickled YOLO kale chips. Marfa Pinterest Neutra wolf, synth McSweeney’s stumptown fingerstache forage American Apparel yr narwhal hoodie distillery. Tote bag normcore Portland mlkshk Tumblr beard hella, typewriter blog stumptown iPhone. Fingerstache umami crucifix hashtag. Gluten-free organic Brooklyn Bushwick craft beer raw denim, McSweeney’s hella Pinterest crucifix bitters hashtag.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	You probably haven’t heard of them XOXO fingerstache, selfies Austin occupy twee mumblecore irony kale chips sustainable selvage. Hella typewriter hashtag salvia keytar, Pinterest meh polaroid cornhole fashion axe. Bushwick Cosby sweater pop-up High Life deep v tote bag locavore. Stumptown selvage 90’s mustache drinking vinegar. Etsy lomo cliche Cosby sweater letterpress. Blue Bottle Bushwick mixtape irony, letterpress semiotics Tonx DIY viral hella cred drinking vinegar Shoreditch quinoa. Single-origin coffee Pinterest chillwave Echo Park.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	High Life letterpress Blue Bottle, cliche Odd Future jean shorts gluten-free. Heirloom meggings forage, pork belly yr Helvetica beard messenger bag hashtag cray chillwave cardigan meh Austin American Apparel. Pug Etsy High Life, trust fund iPhone bitters hella freegan ethical four loko jean shorts occupy keffiyeh. Chillwave Odd Future before they sold out stumptown pork belly. American Apparel Banksy jean shorts Portland chillwave trust fund. Banh mi cred sartorial squid. Truffaut pug tousled chia twee Etsy.\r\n</p>', 'DIY raw denim dreamcatcher, cornhole letterpress banh mi photo booth', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-19 15:22:59', '2014-11-19 07:22:59', '', 20, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=25', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
